<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="MTA87">
<l>iṉṟā vaṟikiṉṟē ṉallē ṉirunilattaic</l>
<l>ceṉṟāṅ kaḷanta tiruvaṭiyai – yaṉṟu</l>
<l>karukkōṭṭi yuṭkiṭantu kaitoḻutēṉ kaṇṭēṉ</l>
<l>ṟirukkōṭṭi yentai tiṟam</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>I do know [him] as of today. Lying in the womb</l>
<l>I worshipped, hands [folded], the sacred feet that had measured</l>
<l>the big earth, going there that day. I saw</l>
<l>the form of our Father in Tirukkōṭṭi.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
